test_large_range:
assert [] == [2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
  Right contains 5 more items, first extra item: 2
  Full diff:
  - [2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
  + []
test_zero_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6] == []
  Left contains 6 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
test_even_range:
assert [1, 3, 5] == [4, 6, 8, 10, 12]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != 4
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: 10
  Full diff:
  - [4, 6, 8, 10, 12]
  + [1, 3, 5]
